{"title":"Kids Ride Shotgun Dirt Hero Balance Bike is a “Scaled-Down Enduro Machine”","link":"https://bikerumor.com/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-is-a-scaled-down-enduro-machine/","date":1680120000000,"content":"<p>Kids Ride Shotgun, better known for their top tube-mounted <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/kids-ride-shotgun-seat-2-0-carries-heavier-kids-now-more-adjustable/\" target=\"_blank\">shotgun child seats</a>, have finally launched the Dirt Hero Balance Bike. In the brand’s eyes, the Dirt Hero represents the next phase in a kid’s riding journey, giving them the freedom to ride singletrack themselves for the very first time. We’ve seen the Dirt Hero up-close a few times now; our verdict? It is a feature-packed and incredibly well thought-through Balance Bike.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We are told, “Every aspect has been considered to ensure kids have the best possible experience when advancing from the driveway to the dirt”.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Kids Ride Shotgun Dirt Hero Balance Bike</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-aged-2-5.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-aged-2-5-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"kids ride shotgun dirt hero balance bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-aged-2-5-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-aged-2-5-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-aged-2-5-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-aged-2-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-aged-2-5-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-aged-2-5-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-aged-2-5.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>The Kids Ride Shotgun Dirt Hero Balance Bike weighs a claimed 4 kg with a 12″ wheelset and without the Magura brake</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Kids Ride Shotgun Dirt Hero Balance Bike is designed for children aged 2-5 years, and has adjustable dropouts allowing for the fitment of 12″ or 14″ wheels. So, as your child grows, so can this Balance Bike. The brand is calling it a “scaled down enduro machine”. As such, it is appropriately fitted with high-volume knobbly tires from Vee Tire Co and a Magura MT4 rear disc brake with rotor guard. The brake runs the HC1 lever, the reach of which can be adjusted for small hands.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-disc-brake-magura.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-disc-brake-magura-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"kids ride shotgun dirt hero balance bike magura disc brake rear rotor guard\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-disc-brake-magura-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-disc-brake-magura-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-disc-brake-magura-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-disc-brake-magura-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-disc-brake-magura-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-disc-brake-magura-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-disc-brake-magura.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, the Dirt Hero is a Balance Bike, but a removable foot pad does offer opportunity for some feet-up riding. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-magura-brake-hc1-lever.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-magura-brake-hc1-lever-800x533.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-magura-brake-hc1-lever-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-magura-brake-hc1-lever-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-magura-brake-hc1-lever-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-magura-brake-hc1-lever-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-magura-brake-hc1-lever-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-magura-brake-hc1-lever-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-magura-brake-hc1-lever.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-mtb-off-road.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-mtb-off-road-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"kids ride shotgun dirt hero balance bike disc brake foot pad\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-mtb-off-road-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-mtb-off-road-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-mtb-off-road-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-mtb-off-road-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-mtb-off-road-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-mtb-off-road-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsrideshotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-kids-mtb-off-road.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>“We’ve noticed a growing number of balance bike families hitting the trails, but we know it can be hard for parents to find a runner bike that’s up to the task. That’s why we set out to create a bike that would open up riding off-road for balance bike kids, enabling them to experience the stoke of mountain biking from an earlier age.”</em> – Dan, Co-Founder.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-geometry.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"233\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-geometry-800x233.jpg\" alt=\"kids ride shotgun balance bike geometry\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-geometry-800x233.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-geometry-297x87.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-geometry-120x35.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-geometry-768x224.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-geometry-1536x447.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-geometry.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>You read that right; this balance bike can even be set up as a mullet</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Kids Ride Shotgun Dirt Hero Balance Bike retails at $340 USD; that’s with the 12″ wheelset and without the Magura brake. The 14″ wheelset and disc brake are optional extras.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s available now, and comes with three customizable top tube skins.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/krs-dirt-hero-balance-bike-mtb-off-road.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/krs-dirt-hero-balance-bike-mtb-off-road-800x534.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/krs-dirt-hero-balance-bike-mtb-off-road-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/krs-dirt-hero-balance-bike-mtb-off-road-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/krs-dirt-hero-balance-bike-mtb-off-road-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/krs-dirt-hero-balance-bike-mtb-off-road-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/krs-dirt-hero-balance-bike-mtb-off-road-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/krs-dirt-hero-balance-bike-mtb-off-road-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/krs-dirt-hero-balance-bike-mtb-off-road.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-washing.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-washing-800x534.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-washing-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-washing-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-washing-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-washing-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-washing-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-washing-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/kidsride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-washing.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://kidsrideshotgun.co.uk/\">kidsrideshotgun.co.uk</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/kids-ride-shotgun-dirt-hero-balance-bike-is-a-scaled-down-enduro-machine/\">Kids Ride Shotgun Dirt Hero Balance Bike is a “Scaled-Down Enduro Machine”</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"63c8d3c694e06695e06d696418f11bd2d0a512f5ffab62433ac1a29e707ad97c","category":"Cycling"}